default&#xa0;default1.7.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn order for academies to have a transformational impact beyond their own schools there needs to be an explicit demand made of them to do so. 
defaultThe current sponsorship programme is a means to achieve this
default. One means of securing this is by providing 
defaultthe incentive of extra-funding to 
defaultsecure capacity. 
defaultWithout this, academies will shy away from 
defaultvolunteering to sponsor for fear
