default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultOur experience 
defaultshows that the DfE academy sponsor unit has no systematic or routine knowledge of where there is capacity in the system. Thus, it is incumbent upon high performing schools to contact them to offer support – it should be the other way round.
